race.comment: BLAINE KEEPING (3) ran the fastest on the card last time scoring by 4 lengths (17.96) at this track. Can continue the winning form. TRAVELLING GEM (7) is progressing well scoring last time out (19.79) at Goulburn and bringing up his 15th career win. Form here sound including seven wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. BLAZING FERRERO (1) ran below best last time finishing fourth (19.99) over 350m at Goulburn in a NG. Solid record here at this trip including 10 wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Cannot be underestimated. AMAZING GEM (2) racing over this distance brings the best out in her.
